      • normalizeUriPath

        public static String normalizeUriPath​(String uriPath)
        Calculate the normalized form of the given uriPath.

        For example: 

        
    /a/b/c/ -> /a/b/c/
    /a/b/c  -> /a/b/
    /a/     -> /a/
    /a      -> /
        Parameters:
        uriPath - path of a URI (as returned by java.net.URI#getPath()
        Returns:
        the normalized uri path
